      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained</strong> <strong>spaghetti</strong> to the pan with a good grind of <strong>pepper </strong>and a knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until the butter has melted and the pasta is coated in the sauce – this is your <strong>smoky garlic king prawn & pea spaghetti</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash more starchy pasta water if your sauce is looking a little dry</p>",
